text: The Hunza-Nagar District is the seventh district of Gilgit Baltistan of Pakistan. The district is made up of Hunza and Nagar. Sikandarabad is the administrative center of this district. Before the announcement of the new district, Hunza-Nagar was part of district Gilgit. Category:Districts of Gilgit-Baltistan
